4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to equip individuals with the skills needed to become cybersecurity specialists, regardless of prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week with a maximum of 16 participants. Students will learn essential topics such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. No previous experience is required, and the course content is available in English and Spanish. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. For further details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop